---
description: i18n locale YAML and frontend export
globs: config/locales/**/*.yml, app/frontend/**/*.tsx, app/frontend/**/*.ts
alwaysApply: false
---
When adding or changing user-visible strings:

- Edit YAML under `config/locales/` (nest by model, e.g. `config/locales/circles/circles.en.yml`). Do **not** edit `app/frontend/lib/locales/*.json`; those files are generated.
- Regenerate frontend JSON with `bundle exec rails i18n:export`.
- For react-i18next plurals, use flat keys in YAML (`foo_one`, `foo_other`) rather than nested `foo: { one:, other: }`, so export does not produce an object that breaks `t("foo", { count })`.
- Dynamic `t()` key paths may require `ignore_unused` in `config/i18n-tasks.yml`. Run `bundle exec rspec spec/i18n_spec.rb` after locale changes.
